| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0038 — Mass File Rename (netwalker)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 8c2431e1-397f-5501-828e-6d2de3b43618"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
